    <description>A six months behavioral lifestyle program composed of 8 sessions; 4 individual consultations and 4 telephonic calls. The cognitive behavior theory (CBT) is the underpinning theory for the lifestyle intervention; hence CBT behavioral strategies like self monitoring and goal setting are used to improve compliance to healthy lifestyle practices</description>
